{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18side", "eventName": "塵影餘音", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "LE-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "骷髏之舞", "storyInfo": "黑鍵與白堊以塵世之音的共振趕走了源石蟲，巫王的陰影卻還籠罩在兩人身上，謎團尚未解開，一切都指向被動過手腳的音樂廳。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g3_slumstreets_night", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_5"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.71}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......呼......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊，我來了，別再拉琴了！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底想做什麼，自殺嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確實在考慮這個問題。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用琴聲將源石蟲吸引過來，然後......將我自己和它們一起燒成飛灰。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，既然你來了......我大概不會再有這樣的機會了。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊......你......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從很小的時候開始，我就知道，自己的體質有些不尋常。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的感染者和我相處時間長了，病情就會變糟。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這個，我和爺爺一起被趕出了當時的住所，開始在村莊之間流浪。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我一直以為，不是所有的感染者都會被我影響，而且，只要相處的時間不長就不礙事。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但爺爺的病終於越來越重，我的第一個幻想破滅了。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，芙蓉告訴我們，這種叫做“假癒”的現象，在我來到夕照區短短幾周之後，就造成了嚴重的後果。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......既然活著就會造成災難，那我還是死了的好。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不怪你！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼可能不怪我呢？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你知道塵世之音嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽你說完，我......終於想起來了。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塵世之音，死於實驗的人，巫王殘黨......還有你。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我全都想起來了。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以這根本就不是你的錯！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "錯在巫王，錯在那些殘黨，錯在格特魯德——但你是無辜的！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了你讓我想起了那些事情，我才知道，這不是什麼與生俱來的體質，而是一場實驗的惡果。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是在聽了你的大提琴之後才想起來的，我才應該向你道謝。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪有什麼但是？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事情已經超出了我們的掌控，我已經連減輕自己的危害都做不到了。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，如果那位伯爵小姐說得沒錯，我本來也時日無多，不如在這裡......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為什麼會上格特魯德的當？就是因為塵世之音是可以轉移的！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我的塵世之音已經是壞的了，就算轉移給你......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不試一試怎麼知道！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你已經決定赴死了，還有什麼好怕的？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想害你。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我真的受害了，你再去替我操心吧。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在這裡，我們來賭一把。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你平時能感受到塵世之音的旋律嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管是演奏還是施術，我都能模糊地感受到塵世之音的存在......一段已經瞭若指掌，但又和我完全沒有關係的，刺耳的旋律。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我感受到的旋律並不刺耳，反而很溫柔——不對，應該說是，和諧的過了頭，到了空洞的地步。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們倆努力去貼合各自感受到的旋律，試著合奏一場吧。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "合奏......可是沒有聽眾啊。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我們有這麼多聽眾呢。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石蟲？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把那個老傢伙留在塵世的旋律演奏給源石蟲聽，我覺得挺好，很人道。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "長笛和大提琴剛一出聲，兩人都察覺到了問題。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "兩段旋律之間幾乎沒有任何共性。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "長笛聲急迫、狂躁、刺耳，忽快忽慢，充斥著將眼前的一切拖入深淵的衝動。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "提琴聲緩慢、憂鬱、空洞，節奏一成不變，彷彿被天災夷平後的大地，一無所有。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但他們還是硬著頭皮，將不成其為合奏的合奏繼續下去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "很快，源石蟲如潮水一般奔湧而來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在漫天的臭氣裡，兩個人生被塵世之音攪得亂七八糟的人在進行一場荒腔走板的合奏，他們的曲譜是腦子裡不知道是否實存的旋律，聽眾則是源石蟲。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "越是這麼想，黑鍵越覺得，自己似乎摸到了塵世之音旋律的尾巴。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他更加用力地吹奏起來，而白堊的琴聲卻越發沉重和空虛。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵，我......", "name": "白堊"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "黑鍵低頭看向白堊，白堊的頭已經軟軟地垂了下去，手卻還在拉琴，琴聲越來越低，越來越接近虛無。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但偏偏此時，黑鍵覺得自己抓住了什麼東西。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "於是他用盡全身的力氣，吹響了最後一個強音。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "白堊也像掙扎似的，重重拉響了大提琴上最粗的那根弦。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "樂聲如同警報般傳揚開去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "剛剛還瘋狂朝二人湧來的源石蟲，此刻卻如同見到了捕食者一般飛快地退去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊......你還、好嗎......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊，醒著嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（沉重的呼吸聲）", "name": "白堊"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......醒著。", "name": "白堊"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣，你還能聽見塵世之音的旋律嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......說實話，甚至更清晰了。", "name": "白堊"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，是我太魯莽了。", "name": "黑鍵"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往好處想，我們剛剛那段合奏把源石蟲趕走了——", "name": "白堊"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等......", "name": "白堊"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊，怎麼了？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你給我買的新衣服——", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_box"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好，沒有髒。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "氣味呢，不好聞吧？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......確實。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，我現在才是真的臭不可聞。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，我以前也曾經把自己搞得一身味道。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#12$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那次，烏提卡高塔不遠處的建築發生了火災，高塔里的侍從不去救火，反而都衝著我來，把我盯得死死的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怕你跑掉？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怕我跑掉，怕我藏起來，怕我葬身火海......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們還怕你死？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高塔上幾乎所有的窗戶都有法術加強過的柵欄和鎖，就是怕我一時想不開跳下去。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可是重要的吉祥物，要是隨隨便便死了，他們吃不了兜著走。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#12$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正，最後火沒有燒到高塔來，只是熏了我一身的煙味。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就穿著那件煙燻過的外套過了半個月，直到天氣轉暖才脫掉那件衣服。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我也想起一些舊事。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和爺爺被趕出一開始住的地方之後，我們就開始在一些比較富裕的村莊之間流浪。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要隱藏好自己感染者的身份，大多數村莊都還算友好。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在小說裡讀到過，農忙時節，友好的村民會在晚上給短工準備香腸和啤酒，讓他們吃飽喝足。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搖頭）", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "友好的村民給我們準備的是幾個小錢，在天黑之前打發我們出村，怕我們偷東西。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒那麼友好的村民給我們準備的，是硬邦邦的黑麵包，還有逼迫我們就範的武器。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一次，我正幫一個村子幹農活。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天氣很熱，我渾身都是汗，就想趁周圍沒人，把衣服鬆一鬆。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在我打定主意脫衣服之前，不遠處突然亂了起來。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爺爺跑過來告訴我趕快跑，說是一個短工以為沒人注意，把袖子捲了起來，露出了手臂上的源石結晶。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "村民們當即把他扔進廢棄的地窖鎖了起來，還要挨個排查其他人。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是爺爺，我可能也已經死在那個地窖裡了。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死——他們會殺死感染者？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用殺，他們也不敢殺。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們只需要等人餓死、結晶化、爆炸......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是早就有善待感染者的法令了嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是在第一次踏入移動城市之後，才知道有這麼一道法令的。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......很......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很......抱歉。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒必要道歉的，你也是被那位伯爵小姐欺騙......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我是說，如果當年，我再勇敢一點——我能，我能在當時站出來，也許你就不用——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你真的沒必要說對不起。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像你剛才說的，錯在製造塵世之音的人，錯在想利用塵世之音的人，但你沒有錯。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我按照自己的想法保護了你......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#2$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......就像你現在想按照自己的想法保護我一樣。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得對。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，白堊。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走，我們去找芙蓉，去找車爾尼先生......會有辦法的，一定會有辦法的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，等到你身上的塵世之音去除了，到那個時候，再來謝我吧。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們走——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#11$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g4_embassy", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊的情況基本穩定，昏厥的原因基本可以確定是中毒。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經救助了不少中毒的患者，他們的體徵和關鍵指標都和現在的白堊類似。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但關於白堊的未來......那位伯爵可能沒有撒謊。他的整體狀況確實來到了危險的邊緣。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你會幫我們的，對不對？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......非常想相信你們。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我需要證據。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕是狀況證據也好，我需要客觀的事實，來證明塵世之音不是臆測，而是迫近的陰謀的一部分——", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老先生？！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您去哪裡了，我們找了您好長時間！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謊言、臆測？", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己說的話就能百分之百確定是真的嗎？", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對白堊說的那些話......你知道嗎，他差一點因為你的那些話，和源石蟲同歸於盡！", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#3$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵，白堊真的......？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（緩緩點頭）", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果黑鍵沒找到他，他已經那麼做了！", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我告訴你，塵世之音是真實存在的，我可以用自己的腦袋擔保！", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#3$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說什麼？！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在沒有時間跟你們解釋，我還有事要辦。", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我必須......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......像你這麼固執的人，我這輩子都沒見過幾個。", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去音樂廳的休息室，你們就什麼都明白了。", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，音樂廳！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#4$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格特魯德說過，為了配合合奏時的法術，她在夕照廳裡做了一些手腳！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我們現在就過去——", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有車爾尼，你們把他也叫上，免得你們兩個誰也說服不了誰。", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得走了。", "name": "爺爺"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_495_1#6$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老先生，您......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵與芙蓉對視了一眼。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們很想懷疑些什麼，但他們已經沒時間了。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}